Title: POWW Catalyst Machine
Selftext: I'm all in on Ammo Inc. Have been for a while. It seems as though there is a new catalyst every other week. I saw the dip before each event. Someone is playing it smart. I bought at each dip. It would be hard-pressed to not become a Bohemian Stock. With the latest, I see the even more upside to sticking with them - AMMO, Inc. Increases Guidance for Fiscal Year 2021 From $58 Million to $62 Million, Reflecting a Projected 319% Year-Over-Year Revenue Growth.
